      <amcr:chranene_udaje>
        <amcr:nazev>Žalov - fence 1 - Left Hradec</amcr:nazev>
        <amcr:popis>Location Left Player. Hradiště Levý Hradec na ostrožně nad levy bank Vltava. A late 9th century church has been documented on the site (but the archaeological research found the foundations are slightly younger). One of the most important centres of the early Czech state. The fortification is only fragmentary. The site is made up of an acropolis with St. Kliment's Church and a long-watched forecourt, and more recently a second forecourt south of the first.</amcr:popis>
      </amcr:chranene_udaje>
